* [content/profile.js](file:///c:/Users/ragha/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/WEB-4/sudharsan-sre/content/profile.js) - Personal summaries, roles, and links.
* [content/experience.js](file:///c:/Users/ragha/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/WEB-4/sudharsan-sre/content/experience.js) - Timelines and project responsibilities.
* [content/skills.js](file:///c:/Users/ragha/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/WEB-4/sudharsan-sre/content/skills.js) - Categorized skills matrix.
* [content/certifications.js](file:///c:/Users/ragha/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/WEB-4/sudharsan-sre/content/certifications.js) - ACCREDITATION credentials list.
* [content/projects.js](file:///c:/Users/ragha/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/WEB-4/sudharsan-sre/content/projects.js) - Case studies and blueprints.
* [content/achievements.js](file:///c:/Users/ragha/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/WEB-4/sudharsan-sre/content/achievements.js) - SLA metrics and counter configurations.
* [content/contact.js](file:///c:/Users/ragha/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/WEB-4/sudharsan-sre/content/contact.js) - Recruiter hubs and endorsements testimonials.

