### SRE Observability Dashboard Features
* **GPU Particles Connected Canvas:** Created a lightweight, performant canvas particles connection grid (`#telemetry-particles-canvas`) drawing slow-drifting node systems that connect/disconnect dynamically in the background to resemble active network architecture.
* **Heartbeat SLA Uptime decimal ticker:** Added a live decimal SLA clock in the header status indicator. The counter dynamically fluctuates at micro-decimals (e.g. `99.99923% SLA`) in real time to mimic live telemetry.
* **Recruiter Telemetry Console Log widget:** Integrated a simulated command log console in the sidebar. It automatically appends active operations logs (`[SYS_OK]`, `Route53 latency check`, `Karpenter scaled down node pool`) with live local timestamps every 4 seconds.
* **Slider Swipe Support:** Added touch gesture tracking (`touchstart`/`touchend`) to the Testimonials slider for mobile devices.
* **Blueprint Zoom touch-panning:** Re-engineered the magnifier zoom modal to support touch scrolling and dragging on mobile screens.

